By Ajena Jafar I would say the scenery. Uganda is a beautiful country curved by nature herself. We may be landlocked but still get our share of tourists.. why? Well because we are blessed. Uganda is blessed with; 2.  The great river Nile its ecosystem. 3. Lake Victoria and its ecosystem.. 4. Lake Bunyonyi and its ecosystem.. 5. Mount Elgon aka the shield of Africa and its ecosystem.. 6. Great Rift Valley and its ecosystem.. There are many more wonderful attractions in Uganda. These have their own unique ecosystems of humans with various cultural orientations, birds and other Savannah based wildlife. Source: Quora